peachq authors and credits
===========================

peachq is a q-language frontend built on the rayforce array engine. The bulk of
the codebase is the rayforce engine, and the project would not exist without it.

The rayforce engine
-------------------
Created by Anton Kundenko <singaraiona@gmail.com>, with contributions from:

  Anton Kundenko   <singaraiona@gmail.com>
  Serhii Savchuk   <ser.vasilich@hotmail.com>
  Hetoku           <volonter84@gmail.com>
  Aspirational     <dovganchin@gmail.com>

(The commit history preserves every upstream author's name and email verbatim;
run `git shortlog -sne` to see the full contribution breakdown.)

The q layer
-----------
The q parser, q datatypes/semantics, lowering pass, registry, formatter, IPC
wire, and build were written by:

  Ryan Hamilton    <ryanhamilton@users.noreply.github.com>

Bundled third-party code
------------------------
  yyjson                              — MIT (see third_party/yyjson/LICENSE)
  q parser (derived from a reference) — Apache-2.0 (see NOTICE)

See LICENSE for the project license (MIT) and NOTICE for third-party terms.
